.30-sheer-swimwear.description:
These bikinis are exotic and bold, with a sexy appeal. Our bikini selection is of the highest quality from offered by the manufacturer Ujena. Styles and cuts vary throughout making it easy for you to find swimwear that suits you. When dry the material is semi-sheer, most visible in the sunlight. Wet each is a fully 
===sheer bikini===
. Many of these pieces are versatile and can easily transition from a day on the beach to a night out. Our sheer halter bikini top makes a perfect camisole. 


Bikini tops are readily available in multiple cuts and sizes, whether your searching for a triangle top, a retro banded halter, or a more concealing swim dress. That same great supply is available in our bottoms, including full coverage, sheer string bottoms, and more. Beyond the classic white and nude colors, a vibrant hot pink, matte black, and sunny yellow are just a few other 
===sheer bikini===
 options to choose from.

.0-swimsuit-sizing.description2:
G-String

  • Sliding adjustable tie
  • Ties at side
  • Minimal back coverage

The UjENA G-string bottom is perfect for the girl who is looking for minimal coverage. Adjustable sliding front and side hip tie allow for a customized fit.

Side tie

  • Side ties
  • Scoop front
  • Full rear coverage

The Side Tie bottom is simple, fun and perfect for any UjENA beach girl. Ties on both hips allow for a perfect fit. Full coverage in back makes this style perfect for all sizes.

Skirted

  • Scoop front
  • Low cut legs
  • Full rear coverage
  • Banded Skirt overlay

The UjENA Skirted bottom is slimming, flattering and sexy! Designed to cover a little bit more, this skirted style bottom is one of our newest and most popular. Banded in the waist to slim and trim.

Colombian “scrunch” tie

  • Side ties
  • Scoop front
  • Scrunch back

The UjENA Colombian “scrunch” tie is fun and practical with a little edge. Ties at both sides and a scooped front give this the typical bikini bottom lookâ¦ but, the added scrunched seam in back will make all UjENA girls backsides look amazing.

Itsy Bitsy

  • Side ties
  • Skimpy fit

The name says it all… the UjENA Itsy Bitsy bottom ties at both hips and has an itsy bitsy amount of coverage in the back.

Wrap Bottom

  • Scooped front
  • High cut legs
  • Full rear coverage
  • Attached belt shirred at back

The UjENA Wrap bottom is the best hip slimming suit a UjENA girl will ever own. The wrap around belt can be tied loose or tight and will conceal and slim the hip area.

Banded Booty Short

  • Banded waistband
  • Booty short cut
  • Full rear coverage

Every girl wants a little Booty Short with a band. Banded waists are the coolest, they slim, trim and conceal while still allowing us to look and feel sexy. The Banded Booty Short is every UjENA girls dream! Perfect for all shapes and all sizes.

Tonga

  • Low cut front
  • Tonga back

If you got it flaunt it… right? The UjENA Tonga is for those of us who are ready to show some skin! Scooped in front and revealing in back.

High Waisted

  • High waisted
  • Full rear coverage

Got a little tummy you would like to cover? The UjENA High Waisted bottom is perfect… it's designed to slim and trim and is cut higher in the waist area to cover just a touch more.

Calypso Bottom

  • V-cut front
  • Shirred panels
  • Mid cut legs
  • Full rear coverage

The Calypso bottom remains a UjENA best seller every season. The V-cut front slims the waistline and hips. Full back coverage. This styles looks great on all shapes and sizes.

Full Scoop

  • Scoop front
  • Full rear coverage

Sometimes it is the simplest of bottoms that look the best! The UjENA Full Scoop dips just a bit in front and fully covers the back side.

Banded Bottom

  • High cut waistline
  • Low cut legs
  • Full rear coverage

The UjENA Banded bottom is a must-have style for every UjENA girl. Available in all sizes, this style slims, flatters, and functions as one of the best style bottoms in the market. Skinny girls, big girls, medium girls will all look amazing in the UjENA Banded bottom.

Top of page

.0-swimsuit-sizing.description:
Banded Halter

  • Halter style
  • Ties at neck and back
  • Banded at bust line
  • Removable pad inserts

The Banded Halter top supports busts of all sizes. It is perfect for an active UjENA girl and offers a full-coverage fit with a sexy edge!

Supportive Halter

  • Halter style
  • 5/8" Supportive Elastic Band at bust line
  • Ties at neck and back
  • Removable pad inserts

The Supportive Halter top fits on busts of all sizes. The supportive elastic band offers a little extra lift for the active UjENA girl.

Calypso Underwire

  • Underwire cups
  • Shirred panels
  • Wide straps
  • Back hook closure
  • Removable pad inserts

The Calypso Underwire top is great on all size busts but most perfect on a full back, full bust body. The underwire will support, lift and enhance the bust line. This top is one of UjENAâs most popular styles.

Colombian Triangle Top

  • Adjustable sliding triangles
  • Ties at neck and back
  • Longer cut triangle
  • Removable pad inserts

The Colombian Triangle Top is ideal for the UjENA girl who loves the traditional triangle style but, is looking for just a touch more coverage. The triangle is cut longer to cover more of the bust area. This style is a hit for the UjENA beach girl buyers.

Classic Twist Top

  • Strapless
  • Twist front
  • Ties at back
  • Removable pad inserts

The Classic Twist Top has been a UjENA favorite for over 25 years. This twist in the front flatters all bust sizes, making a smaller girl look fuller and a fuller bust look great! The slim-cut ties in the back offer a perfect fit.

Long Triangle Top

  • Ties at neck and back
  • Adjustable sliding triangles
  • Removable pad inserts

The Long Triangle top is the ideal top for the UjENA girl who wants some freedom in the fit. The sliding halter-style triangles can be placed in just the right spot for a perfect fit.

Triangle Top

  • Ties at neck and back
  • Adjustable sliding triangles
  • Removable pad inserts

The Triangle Top is simple, sexy and something that belongs in every UjENA beach girlâs wardrobe. Sliding triangles and ties at the neck and back offer a custom fit.

Bandeau Slider

  • Slider front
  • Front neck tie
  • Ties at back
  • Removable pad inserts

The UjENA Bandeau Slider fits great on small and full busts. Smaller busts will look fuller while a larger bust will have support in both the back tie and the lift of the front neck tie. Excellent for a day at the beach or a dip in the pool, this top is sporty and sexy.

Camkini

  • Ties at neck
  • Keyhole neckline
  • Seamed bust line

The Camkini top is great for a UjENA girl with a full bust. The seamed bust line and ties at the neck will lift and support. Fitted in the body for more coverage and a slimming sexy look.

Tankini

  • Waist length style tankini
  • Crisscrossed straps in back
  • Tummy control lining
  • Seam under bust

The UjENA Tankini is the ideal swim top; Supportive in the bustline and loosely cut in the body for a very figure flattering fit. We have added a new feature, the Tummy control lining which controls your tummy giving you a smooth and slimming fit.

Long Banded Halter

  • Halter style
  • Ties at neck
  • Thick band below bust

The Long Banded Halter is one of UjENA's most sought-after styles. The halter gives lift and support while the longer band covers just a touch more in front. The thicker band can be folded over for a slimmer look.

Classic Monroe

  • Twist front
  • Wide halter straps
  • Ties at neck and back
  • Removable pad inserts

The Classic Monroe top is sexy, supportive and functional all in one. It fits best on fuller busts. The twist controls and flatters the bust line while the halter straps add lift and support. Every full-busted UjENA girls loves this top!

Underwire Top

  • Spaghetti straps
  • Light soft padding
  • Removable pad pockets

The Underwire top lifts and supports your bustline. Halter ties at the neck and back allow for a perfect fit. UjENA girls love how their bust line looks in this super flattering top.

   

Top of page
